      <title>Golang源码小试牛刀:Gorm框架源码小探01</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/006golanggorm%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%8A%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81/</link>
